  "A school cafeteria surveys 300 students about meal preference (hot lunch vs. packed lunch) and grade level (9th, 10th, 11th, 12th). The results show: 9th hot=40, 9th packed=35, 10th hot=38, 10th packed=37, 11th hot=30, 11th packed=45, 12th hot=25, 12th packed=50. Which grade level has the highest proportion of packed lunches?": "",
